{"tid":2038490,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"與何鴻燊合照裁走梁天琦 港大：照片經剪裁已補回原照 對造成誤解感到遺憾","createTime":"2020-05-27T15:03:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T15:16:24.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"968ffce5273f33c52f5630863f76bc35ada21e22","tid":2038490,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T15:03:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/rthk_new_c/115028\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frthk_new_c%2F115028&d=YPabaHIeuUhgFn7y0hV32TizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=638bddd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/rthk_new_c/115028</a><br />\n<br />\n港大校長張翔昨日就商人何鴻燊逝世發文致以深切哀悼，新聞稿其中一張何鴻燊與港大學生的合照，本土民主前綫前發言人梁天琦被裁走。港大表示，絕對無意作出審查，並對造成任何誤解，感到遺憾。港大發言人表示，新聞稿及社交媒體所使用的相片，均經剪裁及拼貼，其中一張在2014年銘謝禮拍攝的照片，由於收到意見，已補上原照。<br />\n<br />\n2020-05-27 22:42:25"},{"pid":"de830eea5eee40b7d6f4a624cad2ca4104ee79aa","tid":2038490,"uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T15:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JeXALwd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJeXALwd.jpg&h=bcb8fd51&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d6b2311a665378ff6bee3729faa39e3c2ad5d658","tid":2038490,"uid":143499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T15:04:49.000Z","msg":"諗起史太林喺河邊嗰張合照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歷史真係好恐怖"},{"pid":"0f49be0bf17a2227cde919ad042cecf5f13cde3b","tid":2038490,"uid":224657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T15:05:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4db5d3d9ba2a2bf9f19193bba6094918da386850","tid":2038490,"uid":39010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T15:06:57.000Z","msg":"轉頭俾ar"},{"pid":"16bf369c7be182e4a